       This  module  creates a raster map containing concentric rings around a
       given point.  The cell values are increasing  linear  from  the  center
       point  to  outer  rings.  Minimum  and  maximum radius can be selected.
       Optionally a "donut" ring can be created to use as (binary) filter  for
       _i_._i_f_f_t inverse Fourier transform (apply filter with _r_._m_a_s_k).

